cn.felord.payment.wechat.v3.model.busifavor

类 BusiFavorReceiveConsumeData.AttachInfo

  • java.lang.Object
    • cn.felord.payment.wechat.v3.model.busifavor.BusiFavorReceiveConsumeData.AttachInfo
  • 封闭类:
    BusiFavorReceiveConsumeData

    public static class BusiFavorReceiveConsumeData.AttachInfo
extends Object
    商家券领券事件回调通知解密-发券附加信息

    仅在支付有礼、扫码领券（营销馆）、会员有礼发放渠道，才有该信息

    从以下版本开始:
    1.0.4.RELEASE
    作者:
    felord.cn
